channel.title: How Do I Make The Rule For My Router?
channel.description: I looked at the tutorials, and it didnt help. I dont know how to find the Ip for my router. How do I do it? :confused:[br][size=1]Posted on: January 21, 2007, 12:00:59 PM[/size][hr]Someome please help me

item.title: How Do I Make The Rule For My Router?
item.dc:creator: @Gol_Goroth Gol Goroth
item.description:
@Gol_Goroth wrote:

Press start and go to run, type in cmd. on the screen it opens type in Ipconfig and it will tell you the computer ip and the router.

The one with gate in is the router i.p
